>> source: Tante Myrna Seccia

Brown the @lean ground beef{2%lbs} with chopped @onion{1}, drain and add @garlic{3%cloves}, @cumin{1%tsp}, @coriander{1/2%tsp}, @sugar{3%Tbsp}, @salt{1%tsp}, @pepper{1/2%tsp}, and @accent{1/2%tsp}. Then add @Dutch soy sauce{1/2%cup}.

Make sure meat mixture is cool before you put them in the @empanada pastry{} to fry until golden brown.
